AIM: Write a c program to check the given number is divisible by
3 and 5
Pseudo code :
Begin
Define integer num
Read num
If (num%3==0)
If (num%5==0)
Display (“num is divisible by both 3&5”)
Else
Display (“num is divisible by 3”)
Else if (num%5==0)
Display(“num is divisible by 5”)
Else
Display (“num is not divisible by 3&5”)
